| Task                 | Command/Path                      |
| -- |  |
| Install SSH Server   | `sudo apt install openssh-server` |
| SSH Status           | `sudo systemctl status ssh`       |
| SSH Logs             | `/var/log/auth.log`               |
| Tail Auth Log (live) | `sudo tail -f /var/log/auth.log`  |
| Connect via SSH      | `ssh user@<server-ip>`            |




